    ICfgClassOperationalInfo, ICfgEnum<CfgStructureType>, ICfgNameOperationalInfo
    public final class CfgDescriptionStructureDelta
extends CfgDescriptionStructure
implements ICfgClassOperationalInfo
    CfgDescriptionStructureDelta class is descriptive class for configuration protocol delta structures.

    CfgDescriptionStructureDelta class is derived from the the base CfgDescriptionStructure class. CfgDescriptionStructureDelta also implements ICfgClassOperationalInfo interface.

    See Also:
    CfgDescriptionStructure, CfgStructureType
